00:43:00.410 --> 00:43:02.860
Designers are trained to think
in many of these ways.

00:43:02.860 --> 00:43:05.880
We read publications and
websites and content about

00:43:05.880 --> 00:43:08.210
this stuff, and we think
about it every day.

00:43:08.210 --> 00:43:10.190
