00:53:56.860 --> 00:53:58.390
OSSAMA ALAMI: And we're working
on bringing those

00:53:58.390 --> 00:54:00.478
libraries to the developer
community.

00:54:00.478 --> 00:54:02.190
AUDIENCE: Thank you.

